channel.title: [PI]Rebellion - 1 Year+ Work
channel.description:
So someone keylogged me by asking me for help and sent me to a website that bugged my pc. He stole my work, therefor I am going to release it so everyone knows when they see my content, I created it. -.- Also i dont want people being tricked into paying for my work to some douche. A lot of custom work of mine(NOT custom items), 90% Prestige System, A lot of Re-Written skills, a lot of bug fixes/dupe patches. My combat is far from perfect, we are mainly a pvm, and skilling eco server, so i did not put a huge amount of work into combat.
The kids skype is: so.fishy <DO NOT TRUST.
Credits - Mattsforeal Faris Sanity Scott Graham God(Jake)
-Re-Written Fletching, Crafting, Herblore, Mining, Woodcutting, Smelting, Hunter -Prestige System -Rebellion Point System -Rebellion Shop -Many processes Cycle Based -Server Ticks handled via Task -Resizeable Client -Dicing -Crystal Chest -Prestige Chest -Mystery Eggs -Money for Levels -Achievements -More, and more, and more will add more as i think it up
[IMG]http://www.project-innovation.org/images/updates2.PNG[/img] :hurr:Dont Mind The Kallipso, was old name [IMG]http://www.project-innovation.org/images/WholeSaleWtrMrk.png[/img][IMG]http://www.project-innovation.org/images/PrestigeItemsWtrMrk.png[/img] [IMG]http://www.project-innovation.org/images/PrestigeAbilitiesWtrMrk.png[/img][IMG]http://www.project-innovation.org/images/NewPk.PNG[/img] [img]http://puu.sh/1BQsT.png[/img][img]http://puu.sh/1BeIC.png[/img] [img]http://puu.sh/1u7eD.png[/img] [img]http://puu.sh/1q82W[/img][img]http://puu.sh/1pPN1.png[/img][img]http://puu.sh/1ho7q.png[/img][img]http://puu.sh/GneF[/img][img]http://puu.sh/1pPKw[/img]
There is a lot more than just in those pictures, might add more tomorrow.
To Let You Know: Anti Leech: Must make your own Prestige.java or Buy it, also Must Use Eclipse! No more notepad++ shit All SQL Related Classes were deleted. (Ex: Vote,Highscores) Client is downloaded via launcher, if i get a nice amount of downloads i will release it too. Cache version is stored on your website by cacheversion.txt and need to link it in the client (UpdateCache.java)
Source: [url=http://up.ht/SCpfrt]Download Rebellion.Source.zip @ UppIT[/url] Client: [url=http://www.project-innovation.org/OpenSource/Rebellion%20Client.zip]www.project-innovation.org/OpenSource/Rebellion%20Client.zip[/url] Cache: [url=http://www.project-innovation.org/downloads/rebellionCacheFull.zip]www.project-innovation.org/downloads/rebellionCacheFull.zip[/url]
Flame if you hate, Thank if you like, Rep if you Love
